title: Benchmark Sues to Kick Kalanick Off Board (Audio)
itunes:title: Benchmark Sues to Kick Kalanick Off Board (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Jeff Feeley, Bloomberg News, discusses the lawsuit between Benchmark and Uber in order to get Kalanick off the board of the ride-hailing app. He speaks with Greg Stohr on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Law."

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
